  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK473">
<l>uṭaittam valiyaṟiyā rūkkatti ṉūkki</l>
<l>yiṭaikkaṇ murintār palar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There are many who, ignorant of their (want of) power (to meet it), have haughtily set out to war, and broken down in the midst of it.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
